===國際===
目前國際上較普遍的環境友善計畫是[[能源之星|能源之星]]（Energy Star），由美國於1992年發起，目的是要減少[[溫室氣體|溫室氣體]]的排放。<ref>{{cite web|work=Energy Star|title=About Energy Star|url=http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=about.ab_index|accessdate=2007-07-10|archive-date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224230726/https://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=about.ab_index|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了美國之外<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.energystar.gov/|title=United States Energy Star Home Page|work=Energy Star|accessdate=2007-07-10|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206162056/https://www.energystar.gov/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，歐洲聯盟<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eu-energystar.org/|title=EU Energy Star Home Page|work=Energy Star|accessdate=2007-07-10|archive-date=2018-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708051602/http://eu-energystar.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、澳大利亞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.energystar.gov.au/ |title=Australia Energy Star Home Page |work=Energy Star |accessdate=2007-07-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070703110036/http://www.energystar.gov.au/ |archivedate=2007-07-03 }}</ref>、加拿大、日本、紐西蘭和台灣地区也都有參與計畫。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=partners.intl_implementation|title=Who’s Working With ENERGY STAR? International Partners|work=Energy Star|accessdate=2009-02-03|archive-date=2018-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127161523/https://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=partners.intl_implementation|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===歐洲===
屬於[[歐洲聯盟|歐洲聯盟]]成員以及符合環境友善標準的商品，經審核後會得到一枚生態標籤。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ec.europa.eu/environment/ecolabel/index_en.htm|title=Welcome to the European Union Eco-label Homepage|work=EUROPA|accessdate=2007-07-10|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417111234/https://ec.europa.eu/environment/ecolabel/index_en.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ec.europa.eu/environment/emas/index_en.htm|title=EMAS|work=EUROPA|accessdate=2007-07-10|archive-date=2019-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190505051324/http://ec.europa.eu/environment/emas/index_en.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>除此之外，[[德國|德國]]還會使用{{le|藍色天使 (認證)|Blue Angel (certification)|藍色天使}}認證標籤，<ref name="Type 1">{{cite web |url=http://www.ricoh.com/environment/label/type1/index.html#hun_eco |title=Environmental Labels Type I |accessdate=2007-07-10 |work=Ricoh |archive-date=2018-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215173506/https://www.ricoh.com/environment/label/type1/index.html#hun_eco |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[北歐|北歐]]地區則是使用[[北歐天鵝|北歐天鵝]]認證標籤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.svanen.se/ |title=北歐天鵝官方網站 |access-date=2010-11-14 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418105119/https://www.svanen.se/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===北美洲===
在[[美國|美國]]的[[綠色營銷|綠色營銷]]方面，常出現沒有深入說明的標語，例如僅以「環境友善」一詞標示於商品，卻未說明標準如何。因此常造成環境友善定義上的混亂，但目前已有監管機構為業者提供相關指導。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/grnrule/guides980427.htm |title=Environmental Claims |accessdate=17 November 2008 |work= |publisher=Federal Trade Commission |date=2008-11-17 |archive-date=2008-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081117145015/http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/grnrule/guides980427.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
<ref name=EPAICOU />

在[[加拿大|加拿大]]方面，則是有「[[環境選擇方案|環境選擇方案]]」（Environmental Choice Program）計畫<ref name="Type 1">{{cite web |url=http://www.ricoh.com/environment/label/type1/index.html#hun_eco |title=Environmental Labels Type I|accessdate=2007-07-10 |work=Ricoh}}</ref>，創立於1988年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.environmentalchoice.com/English/ECP%20Footer/About%20the%20Program |work=EcoLogo |title=About the Program |accessdate=2007-07-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070618224105/http://www.environmentalchoice.com/English/ECP%2BFooter/About%2Bthe%2BProgram |archivedate=2007-06-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。只要通過審核，商品均可獲得環境友善的認證標籤。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ns.ec.gc.ca/g7/eco-can.html |title=Environmental Choice (Canada) |accessdate=2007-07-10 |work=Environment Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071125105653/http://www.ns.ec.gc.ca/g7/eco-can.html |archivedate=2007-11-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

